'''Hariz Downside''' was a [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] in the city of [[Hariz]], on [[N'zoth]]. A section of it was reserved for the [[Aramadia (Super Star Destroyer)|''Aramadia'']], [[Nil Spaar]]'s flagship. Other facilities within included shops, troop barracks, hotel and bar.<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
The diagram in ''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]'' misspells the spaceport as "Haziz Downside".<ref name="CCW" />

